 by a perfect harmony of effects, sounds, and surroundings designed to alleviate the stresses of a hectic day.\n\nThe game doesn't require any physical or in-game movement from you. You can play it comfortably both while standing and sitting. And the entire gameplay is exceptionally smooth, enveloping you in a meditative atmosphere.\n\nOur team is preparing numerous new exciting episodes for you to enjoy soon.\n\nEmbark on this engaging adventure and experience the meditative power of VR with a painting journey.", "short_description": "Fantasia Canvas invites you to seamlessly transition from the bustling demands of daily life into an atmosphere of tranquility and relaxation.\n\nColoring vivid miniatures is a truly mesmerizing and engaging experience, complemented by a perfect harmony of effects, sounds, and surroundings designed to alleviate the stresses of a hectic day.\n\nEmbark on this engaging adventure and experience the meditative power of VR with a painting journey."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://fantasia.games/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Fantasia Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://fantasia.games/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3771364559549515"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "de", "ru", "es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "852132063143126"}}]}, "schedule